{"id":250223,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/09/global-voices-突尼斯：日益高涨的种族主义？/","date":"2012-09-04T21:30:13Z","modified":"2012-09-04T21:30:13Z","title":"Global Voices | 突尼斯：日益高涨的种族主义？","content":"<p><p>Frederick Gore Djo Bi于africavox.com上头<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.africavox.com/billet.cfm/8773_vague-de-racisme-depuis-la-revolution-tunisienne.html\" href=\"http://www.africavox.com/billet.cfm/8773_vague-de-racisme-depuis-la-revolution-tunisienne.html\">发表了</a>法文一篇有关突尼斯境内，反非洲黑人（black Africans）种族主义高涨的文章。Bi在他的文章中，引用了来自象牙海岸、自2007年便居住在突尼斯的工程系学生Fabien Siei的说法法文：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>每一天都会有非洲黑人遭受种族辱骂。最常被使用的羞辱字眼是”Guira Guira”，这在当地方言中意思是“大猴子”。对许多突尼斯人来说，我们非洲黑人就是奴隶。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Portnoy\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80E7%AA%81%E5%B0%BC%E6%96%AF%EF%BC%9A%E6%97%A5%E7%9B%8A%E9%AB%98%E6%B6%A8%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%8D%E6%97%8F%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%EF%BC%9F&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F09%2F04%2F11428%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F09%2F04%2F11428%2F&#038;desc=%E7%AA%81%E5%B0%BC%E6%96%AF%EF%BC%9A%E6%97%A5%E7%9B%8A%E9%AB%98%E6%B6%A8%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%8D%E6%97%8F%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%EF%BC%9F\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F09%2F04%2F11428%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F09%2F04%2F11428%2F&#038;text=%E7%AA%81%E5%B0%BC%E6%96%AF%EF%BC%9A%E6%97%A5%E7%9B%8A%E9%